I’ve known @ball4president since I was 10 years old. He was the first new friend I made when moving back to Tampa in ‘97. On a visit to Florida in 2016, I dropped in on one of his comedy sets and knew he was ready for the big stage. He finally moved to LA at the end of 2018 and we’ve created a ton together. I’m so proud of everything he’s accomplished and am honored to be a part of his first special! Many more to come!

Had an amazing time at SISFA Film Festival! Our film 459 received nominations in almost every category and we won for Best Actor and Audience Choice award for the festival! Thank you @storymodefilms for having us! Enjoyed watching all the great films and such an innovative film festival experience. This festival is a game changer! The handcrafted awards are a nice touch! I’ll cherish it forever!
